        <mxCell id="FE9ONLyQqKI_ao41Rp83-3" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;SQ&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Business Manager&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1. How many orders&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(items/pallets) can be handled within a fixed time window &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-inline&quot; data-math=&quot;T&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;102&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;What is the cost per delivered item under different system configurations?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;What percentage of orders are delivered completely and within their specific time window (&quot;On Time, In Full&quot;)?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Order Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;4. Can a new order be accepted immediately without jeopardizing the Service Level Agreements (SLAs) of existing orders?&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;5.&amp;nbsp;How reliable is the system&#39;s &quot;Delivery promise is feasible&quot; statement?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;6.&amp;nbsp; Do high-priority orders actually reach their destination faster than standard orders?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Production Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Is the production process running continuously, or is it being blocked by a lack of logistics support (e.g., full output buffers)?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="58" y="820" width="1122" height="560" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
