        <mxCell id="Bl6462A4p9M2vjgWZpy1-1" value="TODO (Execution Modeling &amp; BDD):&#xa;- Create expanded pan for transport ticketing&#xa;- Split PAN-4 Transport Execution into 2–3 sub-PANs:&#xa;  1) Transport Execution (move/load/unload, routing, congestion)&#xa;  2) Lift / Vertical Transfer (queue, capacity, cycle time, blocking)&#xa;  3) Staging / Hand-off (buffer capacity, zone interfaces, handover policies)&#xa;- For each sub-PAN, create a Desired + Undesired CEN with a clear COI.&#xa;- For each CEN, list key simulation/BDD parameters:&#xa;  * Travel times per zone (stochastic), pick/place durations&#xa;  * Lift capacity, cycle time, queue policy&#xa;  * Staging/buffer capacity, handover rules&#xa;  * Dispatch rules / priorities&#xa;  * Resource counts &amp; availability (forklifts, breaks)&#xa;  * Congestion/blocking/deadlock conditions&#xa;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=14;" parent="1" vertex="1">
